com.spotify.sdk.android.playback

Class NativeSdkPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spotify.jni.NativeObject
      • com.spotify.sdk.android.playback.NativeSdkPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativePlayer

    public class NativeSdkPlayer
extends com.spotify.jni.NativeObject
implements NativePlayer
    Bridge to the SDK's native player. Passes commands from Player to the underlying Spotify playback service.
